(1717, 174, 1, '04 - Normal', 'Strategic Water Management in Settlers Park', 'At a Board meeting in January 2021, the issue of low-lying cottages having almost continuous municipal water while cottages in Polly Shorts had been without water for months. At the Board Meeting in March 2021, it was agreed that Ted Gilfillan would lead a project to develop a Strategic Water and Effluent Management plan.  This would include:&lt;br&gt;Bulk potable water storage&lt;br&gt;Water storage at cottages&lt;br&gt;Control of supply from all potable water sources&lt;br&gt;Rainwater collection&lt;br&gt;Borehole water&lt;br&gt;The Pond&lt;br&gt;Grey water&lt;br&gt;Sewage&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\nThe strategic plan will be divided into phases, projects, and sub-projects.', NULL, 368, '10 - Not specified', 'Document creation', 1, '2021-03-22 05:21:25', '2021-03-29', '2021-03-22 05:23:04', 174, '2021-03-22 05:23:04', '0.00', '0000-00-00', '00:00:00', '0000-00-00', '00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0.00', 38, 1, '2021-05-07 15:47:35'),
