(4097, 260, 2, '04 - Normal', 'Develop a list of PCs in use by staff', 'In order to deploy MS365 to staff, we need to get a feel for what type of PCs we have. If you have a list already, that would be good.\r\nPlease prepare a list of PCs in use by staff.\r\nTo find the data required, visit the PC, select Settings -&gt; About.  Copy the details, create an email to yourself, enter Responsible User and Office where the PC is located, PC Type, and paste the information from Settings -&gt; About.  Send the email.  When back in the office, copy and paste details from the email to the spreadsheet.  Share the spreadsheet with Irene using OneDrive.', 'Data is in an Excel spreadsheet with columns for: Inspection date, Responsible User, Office, PC Type (Laptop/Desktop), Processor, Installed RAM, 32/64 bit, Operating System, Version, OS Build.\r\nThere are at least 22 entries for PCs.', 368, '10 - Not specified', 'Document creation', 1, '2021-10-07 19:04:13', '2021-10-31', '2021-10-07 19:06:48', 522, '2021-10-23 19:24:23', '22.00', '2021-10-29', '00:00:00', '0000-00-00', '00:00:00', '2021-10-30 13:36:49', '0.00', 42, 1, '2021-10-30 13:40:31'),
(4098, 260, 2, '04 - Normal', 'Convert current MS365 licenses to NPO licenses', 'We currently have a monthly subscription for about four MS365 full-price licenses.  We need to terminate these licenses and purchase equivalent NPO licenses via the &quot;onmicrosoft&quot; account.  Please contact 4-Sight and ask them how to do it.  Remember to record details of the User of the full price license (sign-on, password, email details) before changing the license.', 'Each User with a MS365 license is using a free or NPO license from Microsoft.  No further full-price payments are made to Microsoft.', 368, '10 - Not specified', 'Management action', 1, '2021-10-07 19:17:34', '2021-11-04', '2021-10-26 09:30:51', 522, '2021-10-27 12:35:27', '0.00', '2021-11-02', '16:00:00', '0000-00-00', '00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0.00', 42, 1, '2021-10-30 13:37:56'),
(4099, 260, 9, '04 - Normal', 'Identify who needs Windows 10 and MS365', 'Review the spreadsheet listing PCs and their current software and identify those that do NOT have Windows 10 and MS365 installed.  Review this list with Allister and establish what software needs to be installed and which PCs need to be relocated or replaced.', 'Lists should be prepared: Which PCs need to have Windows 10, MS365, and which need to be replaced.  Recommend moving PCs between Users if a non-critical User has a better PC than a critical User.', 368, '10 - Not specified', 'Management action', 1, '2021-10-07 19:49:02', '2021-11-04', '2021-10-26 09:31:30', 522, '2021-10-30 13:39:02', '0.00', '2021-11-02', '16:00:00', '0000-00-00', '00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0.00', 42, 1, '2021-10-30 13:39:02'),
